{"tid":2397631,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實唔係話唔信得星座","createTime":"2021-02-06T14:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T16:34:32.000Z","uid":370062,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a74e7209d0d187df310e9618036d14e7796fb807","tid":2397631,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"我都明呢個世界係有好多人有唔同程度嘅殘障<br />\n亦都明白呢種人比較容易信啲低能嘢<br />\n我知你哋其實都唔想咁嘅<br />\n呢樣嘢係天生嘅<br />\n你哋都控制唔到<br />\n香港係多元社會<br />\n我都唔會話歧視你哋有缺陷<br />\n又或者歧視你哋嘅喜好<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>但係</strong></span></span><br />\n你哋周圍講星座真係好撚煩<br />\n有大把人一樣係智障<br />\n但係人哋都知醜<br />\n識得收收埋埋盡量唔俾人知<br />\n點解你哋班弱智星座撚反而鍾意周圍話人知你哋係智障<br />\n乜你哋唔知醜㗎咩<br />\n你哋唔好因為自己係智障就自暴自棄周圍獻醜啦<br />\n智障都可以有尊嚴㗎<br />\n唔該你哋<br />\n真係真係唔好再周圍講星座啦<br />\n真係好撚煩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b85744fd30281b845c3bbc741e4a5728557f96","tid":2397631,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"拜神、祈福、風水嗰D都係一樣咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf26e0fb5d8c2c899779c25087740797177c787","tid":2397631,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"14b85744fd30281b845c3bbc741e4a5728557f96","tid":2397631,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"拜神、祈福、風水嗰D都係一樣咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:04:08.000Z","msg":"我最近發現耶教唔弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個世界真係有神蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我而家決定信穌哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n神蹟喺度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9296e82137358c99fd007b0db60a65bae4f40c","tid":23976